_:N0aee504856914ad19c1587a7f243beb1 <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The National Space Operations Centre aims to combine space domain awareness procurement opportunities into a single source. However, there may be some procurement that is not captured on this page and it remains the responsibility of interested parties to monitor all relevant procurement information channels.</p>\n\n<p>For specific timeframes, please refer to the tender notice.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"open-procurement\">Open procurement</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"request-for-information-rfi-provision-of-historical-space-object-data-setshttpswwwcontractsfinderservicegovuknotice1d379787-823c-41a0-9caa-d0d8c1f8bc03\"><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.contractsfinder.service.gov.uk/notice/1d379787-823c-41a0-9caa-d0d8c1f8bc03\">Request for Information (RFI): Provision of Historical Space Object Data Sets</a></h3>\n\n<h2 id=\"upcoming-procurement\">Upcoming Procurement</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"nspoc-sovereign-sensor-capability---active-rfhttpswwwfind-tenderservicegovuknotice009745-2026\"><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.find-tender.service.gov.uk/Notice/009745-2026\">NSpOC Sovereign Sensor Capability - Active RF</a></h3>\n\n<h3 id=\"national-space-operations-centre-nspoc-optical-sovereign-sensor-software-osss---find-a-tenderhttpswwwfind-tenderservicegovuknotice009326-2026\"><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.find-tender.service.gov.uk/Notice/009326-2026\">National Space Operations Centre (NSpOC): Optical Sovereign Sensor Software (OSSS) - Find a Tender</a></h3>\n\n<h2 id=\"recently-closed-procurement\">Recently closed procurement</h2>\n\n<p>There are no recently closed procurement opportunities currently to disclose.</p>\n\n<p>This was last reviewed: February 2026</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"links-to-key-procurement-frameworks\">Links to key procurement frameworks</h3>\n\n<p>Key procurement frameworks include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://supplierregistration.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/dps\">Space Enabled and Geospatial Services’ Dynamic Purchasing System (DPS)</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.crowncommercial.gov.uk/agreements\">Crown Commercial Service</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://contracts.mod.uk\">Defence Sourcing Portal (DSP)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/defence-science-and-technology-laboratory\">Defence Science and Technology (DSTL) Serapis Framework</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://rcloud.dstl.gov.uk/\">Defence Science and Technology (DSTL) Research Cloud (R-Cloud)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/national-space-innovation-programme-nsip\">National Space Innovation Programme</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/contracts-finder\">Gov.uk Contracts Finder</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.find-tender.service.gov.uk/\">Find a Tender</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"links-to-key-government-grants\">Links to key Government Grants</h3>\n\n<p>Government grants opportunities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.find-government-grants.service.gov.uk/\">Gov.uk Grants Service</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/defence-and-security-accelerator\">Gov.uk Defence and Security Accelerator</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/apply-for-funding-academic-community-and-educational\">Apply for funding: space-related R&amp;D, innovation and education</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>" .
